      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 20</em>, <em>Adventurer's Armory pg. 5</em>, <em>Advanced Player's Guide pg. 179</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 10 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 3 lbs.</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d3 (small), 1d4 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> x2; <strong>Range</strong> -; <strong>Type</strong> S; <strong>Special</strong> disarm, see text</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Light; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Blades, Light</p><h3>Description</h3><p>You can use this dagger to disarm or sunder enemy blades by catching them in the grooves on the back of the blade and using your weapon as a lever. If you are proficient with this weapon, add a +4 bonus on combat maneuver checks to disarm or sunder bladed weapons while using it.</p>"
